0.3.4 - 08-12-22
  * New configuration option “Auto Setup”. With this option it is possible to run the plugin more than one time at the same page.
0.3.3
  * Feature request : Add new configuration option “Autoplay on Start”. If set , autoplay will start immediately after page load. 
0.3.2
  * Bugfix #1973 : target of internal link use '_blank' as default. Can now overwrite by configuration
0.3.1
  * Fix : change flexform field validation
0.3.0
  * New Feature : Dynamically loading of image sets without page reload (aka ajax). Only with Dam Categories available.
